caption.paragraph:
FIGURE 2.

Adocimus
(
Belonotus
) 
bartenevi


sp. nov.

, orig. Holotype, male from QLD (“… 11 km W of Bald Hill, Mcllwaith Range…”); 
A
: body, dorsal; 
B
: head and thorax, ventral; 
C
: head, dorsal; 
D
: drawing of anterior part of frons, dorsal; 
E
: lateral side of abdominal segments 5 and 6, dorsal; 
F
: male anal sclerite and 
spiculum gastrale
, ventral; 
G
: tegmen, ventral; 
H
: penis trunk, dorsal; 
I
: proximal part of inner sac with armature. Scale bars: 
a
= 1.0 mm to Fig. A; 
b
= 1.0 mm to figs B–C and E–F; 
с
= 0.25 mm to Figs G–I.
